SønderjyskE Logo SønderjyskE is the football department of the Danish multi-sport club Sønderjysk Elitesport. The club plays in the top tier of Danish football, the Danish Superliga. Their home is Sydbank Park in Haderslev. It is the only professional top-level football team in the region of Southern Jutland. Source
